---
---

<section class="firstlook" aria-labelledby="firstlook-heading">
  <figure class="firstlook-media" data-reveal>
    <img
      src="/images/late-desk.jpg"
      width="1536"
      height="1024"
      loading="lazy"
      alt="A business owner working through paperwork alone at a desk, late at night"
    />
  </figure>

  <div class="firstlook-copy" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">
    <h2 id="firstlook-heading">First, we look at how you run.</h2>
    <p>
      A real conversation about the day-to-day. Where the hours go, what gets chased, what only
      you can do. We take that home, come back with what to build first, and lock the plan with
      you before anything ships.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .firstlook {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: calc(var(--section-pad-y) * 1.4) var(--section-pad-x);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(0, 0.95fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .firstlook-media {
    border: 1px solid var(--site-border);
  }

  .firstlook-media img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .firstlook-copy h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.6vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .firstlook-copy p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--site-text-dim);
    max-width: 30rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .firstlook {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding-top: var(--section-pad-y);
      padding-bottom: var(--section-pad-y);
    }
  }
</style>
